T1  - Political foundations of the lender of last resort: A global historical narrative
AU  - Calomiris, Charles W.
AU  - Flandreau, Marc
AU  - Laeven, Luc
JO  - Journal of Financial Intermediation
VL  - 28
SP  - 48
EP  - 65
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2016/10/01/
T2  - Rules for the Lender of Last Resort
